snippet.title: FIFA 20 | Official VOLTA Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
17 global playgrounds and countless ways to express your style. This is VOLTA FOOTBALL in FIFA 20 http://x.ea.com/59323

FIFA 20 launches worldwide September 27 on PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and PC, bringing two sides of The World's Game to life - the prestige of the professional stage and an all-new authentic street football experience in EA SPORTS VOLTA. Pre-order now: http://x.ea.com/59324

Subscribe to see more FIFA 20 videos: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD.

‘Kam Dog' performed by Kamakaze x Massappeals

#FIFA20 #VOLTA #VOLTAFOOTBALL
